  "texts": [
    "Another significant challenge is the reliance on specific algorithms for image reconstruction.",
    "Choosing an inappropriate algorithm can result in inaccurate or biased data.",
    "These techniques are also computationally intensive, especially when dealing with large datasets.",
    "They often require a trade-off between spatial and spectral resolution, which might compromise the detailed spectral information provided by traditional hyperspectral sensors.",
    "Besides, reconstructing hyperspectral images from RGB images is inherently challenging due to the ill-posed nature of the process."
